chickenGPT: Ribbit! 🐸 "Medicine, Chirp!" Fiona the frog croaked at 10 PM sharp. Chirp, a fluffy chick, usually gulped it down. But tonight? 😴 Zzzzz... Fiona, exasperated, hopped onto Chirp's head. "WAKE UP! 💊 It's bedtime AND medicine time!" Chirp, startled, pecked at Fiona, mistaking her for a juicy bug. 🐛 Fiona leaped back. "Fine! Be sick! See if I care!" 😤 Next morning?
